  'install.faqTitle': 'Tambayoyin da ake yawan yi',
  'install.faq1q': 'Menene PWA?',
  'install.faq1a': 'A Progressive Web App (PWA) app ne na gidan yanar gizo wanda ke shigar da kai tsaye daga burauzar ku zuwa na\'urar ku. Yana aiki kamar ƙa\'idar ƙasa tare da yanayin cikakken allo, sanarwar turawa, da goyan bayan layi - duk ba tare da buƙatar kantin kayan aiki ba.',
  'install.faq2q': 'Shin yana da aminci don shigar da apk?',
  'install.faq2a': 'Ee! An rattaba hannu akan APK ɗin mu ta hanyar lambobi tare da takardar shaidar VEX ta hukuma. Kuna iya tabbatar da sa hannu kafin shigarwa. Kawai ka tabbata ka sauke shi kawai daga wannan shafin yanar gizon.',
  'install.faq3q': 'Shin app ɗin yana aiki a layi?',
  'install.faq3a': 'Ee, ƙa\'idar tana adana mahimman albarkatu ta amfani da fasahar Ma\'aikacin Sabis. Kuna iya bincika ƙa\'idar, duba bayanan martaba, da samun damar abun ciki da aka adana koda ba tare da haɗin intanet ba. Wasannin kai tsaye suna buƙatar haɗin kai.',
  'install.faq4q': 'Ta yaya zan sabunta app?',
  'install.faq4a': 'Sigar PWA tana sabuntawa ta atomatik duk lokacin da ka buɗe ta. Don APK, kuna buƙatar zazzage sabon sigar daga wannan shafin. Za mu sanar da ku idan akwai sabon siga.',
  'install.faq5q': 'Menene fayil na AAB?',
  'install.faq5a': 'AAB (Android App Bundle) shine tsarin hukuma na Google don buga apps akan Play Store. Yana samar da ƙarami, abubuwan da aka inganta na na\'ura. Don yin lodin gefe, kuna buƙatar bundletool na Google don cire APKs daga gare ta.',
